The approved tariffs and charges under subsection (1) may include but not limited to—
* a fixed charge in addition to the charge for the actual electricity supplied;
* a charge in respect of the availability of a supply of electricity and such charge may vary according to the extent of supply;
* a rent or other charge in respect of any electricity meter or electrical plant or equipment provided by the licensee;
* a rate or quantum of discount or premium from the approved tariff in respect of certain type of consumers or public purposes as determined by the Minister; and
* a rate or quantum of payment, charge or levy of any sum pursuant to any other written law or any guidelines issued by the Commission.

